  "description": {
    "canonical": "Sentient tech merges with Corpus design to deliver this lethal sidearm. Fully automatic, it fires ricocheting, homing projectiles that release small clouds of 毒气Gas on impact. Alt-fire to release the entire magazine without homing as a single burst.",
    "display": "Sentient 科技与 Corpus 设计的结合，发展出这款致命的次要武器。该武器为全自动，可射出跳飞式、自动导引的弹幕，子弹在撞击时会释放出小一股 毒气毒气。次要射击为可在单次射击中释放剩余的弹药。",
